==English==
===Noun===
'''Fix'''
#a solution eg to a [[bug]] or programming problem
#a difficult situation or dilemma
#a serving of an addictive drug to an addict

====Translations====
*{{msg:fi}}: [[korjaus]] (1), [[fiksaus]] (''slang'') (1)
*Swedish: fix (1)

===Verb===
'''to fix'''
#to [[mend]] or [[repair]]
#to [[attach]]
#to make a contest unfair to benefit one contestant, usually before the content happens
#to render an animal--especially a pet--infertile

====Translations====
*{{msg:fi}}: [[korjata]] (1), [[kiinnittää]] (2)
*Swedish: [[fixa]] (1)

